Create Measures 11

Step 1 .  Create Measures 

                 1 . Create  a new  table  called Measure Values by click  on Modeling    in power BI  Desktop

                2.  Create new Measure by right click  on measure values table or by  click  on  Modeling  in power desktop

                3.   Cope and Paste  this  DAX  formula  in to new measure one at time  and Click "enter" or  click check sign

               Total Suspected = SUM('Number Of Suspected Cases'[Suspected])

Total Confirmed = SUM('Conformed Cases'[Confirmed Casess])

Total Death = SUM('Conformed Deaths'[Deaths])

The above three measures calculated the total Ebola suspected , Ebola confirmed and Ebola Death between 2014 and 2016

After that created new Measure to calculated the last 12 Months. To do this use this DAX formula
A. TTM_Suspected =
VAR CurrentDate = MAX('Calendar'[Date])
VAR PreviousDate = DATE(YEAR(CurrentDate),MONTH(CurrentDate)-12,DAY(CurrentDate))
VAR Result =
CALCULATE(
[Total Suspected],
FILTER(
'Date',
'Date'[Date]>= PreviousDate && 'Date'[Date]<= CurrentDate
)
)
RETURN
Result

B. TTM_Confirmed =
VAR CurrentDate = MAX('Calendar'[Date])
VAR PreviousDate = DATE(YEAR(CurrentDate),MONTH(CurrentDate)-12,DAY(CurrentDate))
VAR Result =
CALCULATE(
[Total Confirmed],
FILTER(
'Conformed Cases',
'Conformed Cases'[Date]>= PreviousDate && 'Conformed Cases'[Date]<= CurrentDate
)
)
RETURN
Result
C. TTM_Death =
VAR CurrentDate = MAX('Calendar'[Date])
VAR PreviousDate = DATE(YEAR(CurrentDate),MONTH(CurrentDate)-12,DAY(CurrentDate))
VAR Result =
CALCULATE(
[Total Death],
FILTER(
'Date',
'Date'[Date]>= PreviousDate && 'Date'[Date]<= CurrentDate
)
)
RETURN
Result

1. TTM_Suspected/Months = DIVIDE([TTM_Suspected],DISTINCTCOUNT('Date'[YearMonthShort]),0) + 0

2. TTM_Confirmed/Months = DIVIDE([TTM_Confirmed],DISTINCTCOUNT('Date'[YearMonthShort]),0) + 0

3. TTM_Death/Months = DIVIDE([TTM_Death],DISTINCTCOUNT('Date'[YearMonthShort]),0) + 0

4. TTM_MoM Suspected =
VAR __PREV_Month = CALCULATE([TTM_Suspected/Months], DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, MONTH))
RETURN
    DIVIDE([TTM_Suspected/Months] - __PREV_Month, __PREV_Month)+0

5. TTM_MoM Confirmed =
VAR __PREV_Month = CALCULATE([TTM_Confirmed/Months] , DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, MONTH))
RETURN
    DIVIDE([TTM_Confirmed/Months]- __PREV_Month, __PREV_Month)+0

6. TTM_MoM Death =
VAR __PREV_Month = CALCULATE([TTM_Death/Months] , DATEADD('Date'[Date], -1, MONTH))
RETURN
    DIVIDE([TTM_Death/Months] - __PREV_Month, __PREV_Month)+0

Indicator MOM Suspected = IF([TTM_MoM Suspected]<0, UNICHAR(9660),UNICHAR(9650))
Indicator MOM Confirmed = IF([TTM_MoM Confirmed]<0, UNICHAR(9660),UNICHAR(9650))
Indicator MOM Death = IF([TTM_MoM Death]<0, UNICHAR(9660),UNICHAR(9650))


To Create all the above measures , i.e. the measures that calculate the 12 moths create one more calendar table and leave
with out connect to any table.
